SELECT DATE_TRUNC('month', create_date) as month, COUNT(*) FROM tb_partner_product WHERE create_date IS NOT NULL AND create_date > '1900-01-01' GROUP BY month
SELECT DATE_TRUNC('month', create_date) as month, COUNT(DISTINCT partner_id) FROM tb_partner_product WHERE create_date IS NOT NULL AND create_date > '1900-01-01' GROUP BY month
SELECT AVG(DATE_PART('day', CURRENT_DATE - create_date)) FROM tb_partner_product WHERE create_date IS NOT NULL AND create_date > '1900-01-01'
SELECT AVG(DATE_PART('day', CURRENT_DATE - MIN(create_date))) FROM tb_partner_product WHERE partner_id IS NOT NULL AND create_date IS NOT NULL AND create_date > '1900-01-01' GROUP BY partner_id
SELECT product, COUNT(*) FROM tb_partner_product WHERE product IS NOT NULL GROUP BY product ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT partner_id, COUNT(*) FROM tb_partner_product WHERE partner_id IS NOT NULL GROUP BY partner_id ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT DATE_TRUNC('month', create_date) as month, COUNT(*) FROM tb_partner_product WHERE create_date IS NOT NULL AND create_date > '1900-01-01' GROUP BY month ORDER BY month
SELECT DATE_TRUNC('month', create_date) as month, COUNT(DISTINCT partner_id) FROM tb_partner_product WHERE create_date IS NOT NULL AND create_date > '1900-01-01' GROUP BY month ORDER BY month
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM tb_partner_product WHERE create_date IS NOT NULL AND create_date > '1900-01-01' AND create_date < DATE_TRUNC('year', CURRENT_DATE) - INTERVAL '1 year'
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT partner_id) FROM tb_partner_product WHERE create_date IS NOT NULL AND create_date > '1900-01-01' AND create_date < DATE_TRUNC('year', CURRENT_DATE) - INTERVAL '1 year'
